name: Digital Snapshot #1 Infinite
description: I've been intrigued by 1/1 NFT's and the way that they are such a rare art piece when you could create endless copies of the same thing. This then made me think about photography and polaroids. The most common 1/1 in photography. So with this collection I decided to merge both concepts and make it my own. Each NFT will be available as a 1/1 as a digital snapshot I have created from my own work.
